---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Uddin Investment Ltd">
  

  <!-- Privacy Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-12 border-b-2 border-slate-100 pb-8 text-center md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4 italic decoration-blue-600 underline underline-offset-8">Privacy <span class="text-blue-600">Policy</span></h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm italic">Compliance with Data Protection Act 2018 & GDPR</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed italic font-medium">
        
        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 italic border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4 uppercase tracking-tight">1. Overview</h2>
          <p>
            Uddin Investment Ltd ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our property management services or visit our website <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">uddininvestmentltd.com</span>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 italic border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4 uppercase tracking-tight">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect and process the following data about you:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-3 mt-4 decoration-blue-300">
            <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Full name, title, and proof of identity.</li>
            <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Email address, phone numbers, and residential address.</li>
            <li><strong>Property Data:</strong> Address of the investment property, ownership details, and safety certificates.</li>
            <li><strong>Communication Data:</strong> Records of correspondence when you contact our team for valuations or management queries.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 italic border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4 uppercase tracking-tight">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p>Your information allows us to provide professional property services, including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-3 mt-4">
            <li>Providing accurate rental valuations for our Guaranteed Rent scheme.</li>
            <li>Managing tenancies and HMO compliance on your behalf.</li>
            <li>Communicating with local authorities across London and Essex regarding property tenders.</li>
            <li>Organizing maintenance and repairs through our vetted contractors.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 4 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 italic border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4 uppercase tracking-tight">4. Data Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information only with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-3 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Local Authorities:</strong> For the purpose of placing tenants under our Guaranteed Rent contracts.</li>
            <li><strong>Contractors:</strong> To facilitate proactive maintenance and emergency repairs.</li>
            <li><strong>Regulators:</strong> If required by law or professional industry bodies.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 5 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 italic border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4 uppercase tracking-tight">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We have implemented high-level security measures to prevent your personal data from being accidentally lost, used, or accessed in an unauthorized way. Access to your personal data is limited to employees and partners who have a professional "need to know."
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 6 -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 italic border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-4 uppercase tracking-tight">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Under GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-8 space-y-3 mt-4">
            <li>The right to request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li>The right to request correction or erasure of your data.</li>
            <li>The right to withdraw consent at any time where we are relying on consent to process your data.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Section 7 -->
        <section class="bg-slate-50 p-10 rounded-[40px] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 italic underline decoration-blue-600 underline-offset-4">Contact Our Data Team</h2>
          <p class="text-sm italic mb-6">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please reach out:</p>
          <div class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 space-y-2 italic uppercase tracking-widest">
            <p>Data Protection Officer</p>
            <p>UDDIN INVESTMENT LTD</p>
            <p class="text-blue-600">info@uddininvestmentltd.com</p>
            <p>5 Elm Lawn Close, Uxbridge, UB8 1NX</p>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Subtle smooth font rendering */
  p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
</style>